posting_body: ['The Barnum, managed by Steven Scott Management', '1711 County Road E East', 'White Bear Lake, MN 55110', 'show contact info', 'Opening Spring of 2021, The Barnum Apartments offers brand-new one and two-bedroom apartments in White Bear Lake, MN, created to fit your lifestyle needs.', 'Stop by today for a tour!', 'This two bedroom two bathroom accessible apartment features a fully equipped kitchen with an island, entry closet, ensuite bathrooms, and a washer/dryer!', 'This apartment requires a $500 deposit.', 'VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Monday 9:00am - 5:00pm', 'Tuesday 9:00am - 5:00pm', 'Wednesday 9:00am - 5:00pm', 'Thursday 9:00am - 5:00pm', 'Friday 9:00am - 5:00pm', 'Saturday 10:00am - 4:00pm', 'Apartment Features', '* Dishwasher', '* Quartz Countertops', '* Walk-in Closet', '* Breakfast Bar', '* Stainless Steel Appliances', '*', 'Roommate Friendly Floor Plan', '* Linen Closet', '* Refrigerator, Microwave, Dishwasher & Electric Stove', '* Central Heat and Air', '* Disposal', '* Window Coverings', '* Wood-Like Floors', '* Private Patio or Private Balcony (on select apartments)', '* Pre-wired for internet and cable', '* Air Conditioning', '* Vertical Blinds', '* Microwave', '* Kitchen Island', '* Electric Stove', '* Washer and Dryer in unit', '[#9345833]']
